APPENDIX C: Keyboard shortcuts

These are the standard keyboard shortcuts provided with the Soundstudio. To
change them or add more, use the Keyboard Shortcuts window (Settings menu).

C.1 Editing shortcuts

Esc             Edit mode on/off
